BA_JAIL_CRATEEXE - by CRATE.exe

This map is a normal Jailbreak map like all the other. I didnt really put to much effort in at the beginning but a friend of mine told me to make it look better and thanks to his assesment I could improve the map to something better than before. I hope you will enjoy the map

***Fixes***

-Added more players
-Now there is lighting (Thank you Olli3 :D)
-A lot of places to rebell
-Water and vent fix
-Displacement
-Light
-Now with alert system
-Bigger vent system

***New***

-Another pool for more fun
-More walls so its not to easy to kill
-A little bit more weapons
-More airlocks
